ursrecords/rep-graduates/|title=Rep Graduates|publisher=NYC Database|date=2016-09-15|accessdate=2016-09-15}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[http://www.qa.rabbitohs.com.au/team/profiles/wallace_tangiiti.html South Sydney Rabbitohs profile]\n*[https://www.nrl.com/telstrapremiership/playerstats/playerprofile/tabid/10898/clubid/111/playerid/6793/seasonid/43/default.aspx NRL profile]\n*[http://websites.sportstg.com/team_info.cgi?action=PSTATS&pID=196207033&client=7-7901-138462-258059-18828870 Leaguenet profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tangiiti, Wallace}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Australian people of Cook Island descent]]\n[[Category:Australian rugby league players]]\n[[Category:North Sydney Bears NSW Cup players]]\n[[Category:Cook Islands national rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:Rugby league hookers]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Sydney]]\n\n\n{{Australia-rugbyleague-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}}\n{{Use Australian English|date=April 2018}}\n{{Infobox rugby league biography\n|playername     = Wallace Tangiiti\n|fullname       = Wallace Tangiiti\n|image          = Wallace Tangi'iti 2015 Kukis.jpg\n|image_size     =\n|position       = {{rlp|HK}}\n|birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1995|10|16}}\n| birth_place  = [[Sydney]], [[New South Wales]], Australia\n|height         = {{convert|190|cm|ftin|abbr=on|order=flip}} \n|weight         = {{convert|100|kg|stlb|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| club1        = \n| year1start   =\n| year1end     = \n| appearances1 = \n| tries1       = \n| goals1       = \n| fieldgoals1  = \n| points1      = \n| teamA        = [[Cook Islands national rugby league team|Cook Islands]]\n| yearAstart   = 2015-16\n| yearAend     = \n| appearancesA = 2\n| triesA       = 0\n| goalsA       = 10\n| fieldgoalsA  = 0\n| pointsA      = 10\n|updated        = 15 September 2016\n|source         = <ref>[http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/playe